      "text": "翻唱：王小帅（王所长）",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 12.432,
      "time_str": "00:12.432",
      "text": "你最近不说话",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 20.334,
      "time_str": "00:20.334",
      "text": "怎么了为什么",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 24.339,
      "time_str": "00:24.339",
      "text": "是不是有很多事",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 27.334,
      "time_str": "00:27.334",
      "text": "让你不快乐",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 31.838,
      "time_str": "00:31.838",
      "text": "听说你最近很孤单",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 36.589,
      "time_str": "00:36.589",
      "text": "有点乱",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 39.086,
      "time_str": "00:39.086",
      "text": "有点慌",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 42.104,
      "time_str": "00:42.104",
      "text": "可是我却不能够在你的身旁",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 48.851,
      "time_str": "00:48.851",
      "text": "你想要的我却不能够给你我全部",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 52.6,
      "time_str": "00:52.600",
      "text": "我能给的却又不是你想要拥有的",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 56.851,
      "time_str": "00:56.851",
      "text": "我们不适合也不想认输",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 60.598,
      "time_str": "01:00.598",
      "text": "好几次我们抱着彼此都是想要哭",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 64.351,
      "time_str": "01:04.351",
      "text": "你常解释这样的一切都只是开始",
